priority : sync phases > sync waves > resource kind > resource name
sync phases:
1-pre-sync
2-sync(default)
3-post-sync , sync-failed
sync waves:
an integer (negative or positive)
default is 0
the smaller the number is the higher priority
hook deletion policies :
HookFailed
HookSucceeded
BeforeHookCreation (default) : deletes the old resource before creating the new one of same kind/name